<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>회원가입</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h2>회원가입</h2>
    <form action="/signup" method="post">
        <p><label>아이디 : <input type="text" name="userid"></label></p>
        <p><label>비밀번호 : <input type="password" name="password"></label></p>
        <p><label>이름 : <input type="text" name="name"></label></p>
        <p><label>나이 : <input type="number" min="1" max="150" name="age"></label></p>
        <p><button type="submit">회원가입</button></p>
        <p>이미 계정이 있으신가요? <a href="/login">로그인하기</a> | <a href="/">홈으로</a></p>
    </form>
</body>
</html>